ry at the Africa-Oceania Qualifier held in March in Alexandria, Egypt.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 1010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 879, \"end\": 884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999983834917989, \"rank\": 1.6165106135998043e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 992, \"end\": 1002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandria\", \"score\": 0.9998590632111918, \"rank\": 0.00014093149631453673, \"text\": \"Alexandria\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandria\"}, {\"begin\": 1004, \"end\": 1009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7717225579087488, \"rank\": 0.2953885093820245, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Akazawa\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 857}, {\"ngram\": \"his ticket\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 875}, {\"ngram\": \"the 65-kilogram weight class\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 916}, {\"ngram\": \"an emotional victory\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 942}, {\"ngram\": \"the Africa-Oceania Qualifier\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"March\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Falling behind in the first period against his Guinea-Bissau opponent, he came back to win by fall in the second period, which he topped off with a scream of triumph.\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1177, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1058, \"end\": 1071, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guinea-Bissau_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9992169187460573, \"rank\": 0.0007836949462722236, \"text\": \"Guinea-Bissau\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q